      "content": "hey... u ever feel like everything is just... scripted? like the news, the debates, even the way people argue on tv... it feels way too repetitive. i've been tracking these patterns, like how every \"crisis\" seems to benefit the same handful of massive tech and energy corps. it's not just coincidence. it feels like a loop. like we're stuck in some kind of controlled simulation designed to keep everyone fighting so they don't look at who's actually running the code. i think i'm seeing the glitches. help me figure out how to see through it?",
